relevant_findings.general: Alert and oriented, no acute distress, conversant and interactive. Well appearing.
relevant_findings.HEENT: Sclerae anicteric, mucous membranes moist, oropharynx is clear.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no audible murmurs.
relevant_findings.pulmonary/chest: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, respirations are unlabored on room air.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, nondistended, RUQ tenderness, positive sign, no rebound tenderness or peritoneal signs.
relevant_findings.extremities: No lower extremity edema, distal extremities feel warm and appear well-perfused.
